name: Ramen Yatai
description:
i never got a chance to eat at one of these because I was too shy to talk to the vendor - I didn't think my Japanese was good enough.They would set up yatais or these little Japanese food carts up in the city around 5pm- I loved seeing the ones next to the rivers and canals when I stayed in Fukuoka. 
 
I heard that they were slowly dying out (not sure if this is true) so this is my way of trying to capture what that experience would have been like. 

i wanted to put more details but I was reaching the memory limit-- so hopefully I can do a drawover of the scene I wanted to create.
